 rt_row_style="default-style" rt_row_borders="" rt_row_shadows="" rt_row_paddings="true" rt_bg_effect="classic" rt_bg_image_repeat="repeat" rt_bg_size="cover" rt_bg_position="right top" rt_bg_attachment="scroll" rt_bg_video_format="self-hosted"][vc_column rt_column_shadow="" rt_bg_image_repeat="repeat" rt_bg_size="auto auto" rt_bg_attachment="scroll"][vc_column_text]<img class="margeimg" src="http://www.visionfuture.fr/_img/une_info.jpg" align="right" />\r\n<h2>PLUS LOIN QUE LES LUNETTES ET LENTILLES</h2>\r\nLa correction laser a un avantage supplémentaire par rapport aux lunettes ou lentilles, c\'est celui de pouvoir corriger encore plus précisement la vision, en prenant en compte par exemple, de petites irrégularités de l\'oeil (aberration optique), ce qui augmente encore le degré de netteté de la vision corrigée.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row rt_row_background_width="fullwidth" rt_row_content_width="default" rt_row_style="default-style" rt_row_borders="" rt_row_shadows="" rt_row_paddings="true" rt_bg_effect="classic" rt_bg_image_repeat="repeat" rt_bg_size="cover" rt_bg_position="right top" rt_bg_attachment="scroll" rt_bg_video_format="self-hosted"][vc_column rt_column_shadow="" rt_bg_image_repeat="repeat" rt_bg_size="auto auto" rt_bg_attachment="scroll"][vc_separator css_animation="bounceIn" style="style-4"][vc_column_text css_animation="flipInX"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">NOUVEAU : appel d’urgence pour les opérés <b>06 04 98 68 73</b></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator css_animation="bounceIn" style="style-4"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Questions', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '232-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-05-20 18:52:44', '2017-05-20 16:52:44', '', 232, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/05/20/232-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
